Summary of Amendments Adopted by House
The Committee Amendments Proposed by House Committee on Judiciary to the original
bill:
1. Provide that court reporter fees for civil and non-indigent criminal cases may be
$6 per 32-line page transcript and up to $2 per page per certified copy reported.
2. Provide that court reporter fees for criminal indigent cases may be a fee not to
exceed $3.50 per 32-line page transcript and $1 per page per certified copy
reported.
3. Provide that a court reporter may charge for expedited transcription at the
following rates: twice the allowable per-page rate for delivery within 24 hours,
the allowable per-page rate plus $3 per page for delivery within 48 hours, and the
allowable per-page rate plus $1 per page for delivery within five days.
